1
00:00:34,180 --> 00:00:35,940
=The Embroidered Truth=

2
00:00:43,240 --> 00:00:44,359
That was close today.

3
00:00:45,399 --> 00:00:48,280
The worst is yet to come.

4
00:00:48,880 --> 00:00:49,840
Instead of this,

5
00:00:49,880 --> 00:00:51,479
I'll send a pigeon message

6
00:00:51,560 --> 00:00:51,960
for help.

7
00:00:51,960 --> 00:00:52,560
No need.

8
00:00:54,280 --> 00:00:56,320
Since I have a chance
to fix this myself,

9
00:00:56,439 --> 00:00:58,399
I won't let others do it for me.

10
00:00:58,880 --> 00:00:59,880
I get it.

11
00:01:00,119 --> 00:01:02,200
Killing the enemy yourself is best.

12
00:01:02,479 --> 00:01:05,280
But why bring Wu Lian back to the manor?

13
00:01:07,319 --> 00:01:09,239
I want to expose him

14
00:01:09,519 --> 00:01:11,439
layer by layer in front
of the Princess Consort.

15
00:01:11,840 --> 00:01:14,480
By then, even if she wants
to protect him,

16
00:01:14,799 --> 00:01:16,359
it'll be too late.

17
00:01:23,860 --> 00:01:27,780
=Episode 8=

18
00:01:29,640 --> 00:01:30,760
Lady Cheng'en, you know

19
00:01:31,040 --> 00:01:33,040
the Princess Consort needs my hands

20
00:01:33,280 --> 00:01:35,680
to embroider her Flower Festival gown.

21
00:01:35,799 --> 00:01:37,000
Of course I know that.

22
00:01:37,840 --> 00:01:39,680
That's why I won't hurt your fingers.

23
00:01:39,879 --> 00:01:41,719
I just need you to clench your fist

24
00:01:41,920 --> 00:01:43,159
tightly, Master Wu.

25
00:01:43,439 --> 00:01:44,599
Is that too much to ask?

26
00:01:47,079 --> 00:01:49,560
Wu Lian, do you accept your punishment?

27
00:01:54,920 --> 00:01:56,239
I accept my punishment.

28
00:01:57,000 --> 00:01:58,680
Then don't blame me for being harsh.

29
00:02:00,680 --> 00:02:01,480
No!

30
00:02:02,480 --> 00:02:03,680
My master's hands

31
00:02:03,840 --> 00:02:05,680
can't be harmed by a servant!

32
00:02:06,439 --> 00:02:07,680
Even though you're a noble lady,

33
00:02:07,719 --> 00:02:08,599
you can't just...

34
00:02:10,520 --> 00:02:12,360
The Princess Consort's gown
isn't finished.

35
00:02:12,599 --> 00:02:13,960
If his hands are injured,

36
00:02:14,080 --> 00:02:15,280
he'll never embroider again.

37
00:02:15,719 --> 00:02:18,879
Even you can't take that blame.

38
00:02:19,039 --> 00:02:19,840
Master Wu.

39
00:02:21,000 --> 00:02:24,000
Your lapdog wasn't leashed
and disrespected me.

40
00:02:24,439 --> 00:02:26,360
How should I punish you?

41
00:02:29,840 --> 00:02:30,840
Your Highness.

42
00:02:30,879 --> 00:02:32,280
Lady Cheng'en, she...

43
00:02:32,280 --> 00:02:33,240
What's the panic?

44
00:02:33,800 --> 00:02:36,080
Did she try to kill Wu Lian?

45
00:02:36,120 --> 00:02:37,120
Not exactly.

46
00:02:37,719 --> 00:02:39,719
But she wants to hurt his hands.

47
00:02:40,680 --> 00:02:41,840
Hurt his hands?

48
00:02:42,280 --> 00:02:43,639
That's a disaster!

49
00:02:43,719 --> 00:02:45,840
Your Highness's gown isn't finished yet!

50
00:02:47,520 --> 00:02:49,199
If you don't want to be punished,

51
00:02:49,400 --> 00:02:50,919
just say so.

52
00:02:51,319 --> 00:02:53,199
Don't use your lapdog to stop me.

53
00:02:53,479 --> 00:02:55,240
Aren't you afraid I'll kill him?

54
00:02:55,639 --> 00:02:56,919
If you want my life, Lady Cheng'en,

55
00:02:57,240 --> 00:02:58,159
take it.

56
00:02:58,719 --> 00:03:00,280
My worthless life means nothing.

57
00:03:00,680 --> 00:03:03,759
But my master is priceless

58
00:03:03,879 --> 00:03:05,280
in Jinxiu City.

59
00:03:06,319 --> 00:03:08,759
Priceless? Him?

60
00:03:08,879 --> 00:03:09,680
Wu Xin.

61
00:03:12,479 --> 00:03:14,360
Lady Cheng'en is noble.

62
00:03:15,120 --> 00:03:17,240
So what if I lose my hands?

63
00:03:17,319 --> 00:03:20,599
Upsetting Lady Cheng'en is far worse.

64
00:03:25,759 --> 00:03:26,560
Xiaojiu.

65
00:03:27,520 --> 00:03:29,479
Since Master Wu has confessed,

66
00:03:29,719 --> 00:03:32,680
I'll spare him today.

67
00:03:33,000 --> 00:03:33,800
Lady Cheng'en!

68
00:03:33,919 --> 00:03:34,520
Xiaojiu.

69
00:03:35,000 --> 00:03:37,919
Thank you for sparing my hands,
Lady Cheng'en.

70
00:03:38,199 --> 00:03:39,960
I'll embroider the gown
for Her Highness.

71
00:03:40,280 --> 00:03:41,400
We're really letting him go?

72
00:03:42,039 --> 00:03:43,680
The Princess Consort is here!

73
00:03:47,199 --> 00:03:47,919
Master.

74
00:03:48,000 --> 00:03:48,680
How dare you!

75
00:03:49,240 --> 00:03:49,800
Master.

76
00:03:52,080 --> 00:03:53,360
Help him up quickly.

77
00:03:58,280 --> 00:03:59,680
Greetings, Wenyue.

78
00:03:59,879 --> 00:04:00,800
I'm sorry to disturb you.

79
00:04:01,039 --> 00:04:01,919
Please forgive me.

80
00:04:02,639 --> 00:04:04,360
Your Highness, thank goodness
you're here!

81
00:04:04,479 --> 00:04:06,159
Please save my master!

82
00:04:06,240 --> 00:04:06,879
Wu Xin.

83
00:04:08,479 --> 00:04:09,280
Your Highness.

84
00:04:10,120 --> 00:04:11,599
I was in the wrong first.

85
00:04:11,800 --> 00:04:12,800
It's not Lady Cheng'en's fault.

86
00:04:13,319 --> 00:04:15,479
Even if she wanted my hands,

87
00:04:16,040 --> 00:04:17,920
I'd give my life without complaint.

88
00:04:18,199 --> 00:04:20,600
Send for the manor physician! Now!

89
00:04:21,120 --> 00:04:21,839
Yes.

90
00:04:23,439 --> 00:04:24,240
Ruoheng.

91
00:04:24,720 --> 00:04:27,480
I spoil you because we're like sisters,

92
00:04:27,839 --> 00:04:29,319
but today, you've acted disgracefully

93
00:04:29,319 --> 00:04:30,160
and without restraint.

94
00:04:30,519 --> 00:04:32,360
I'm grounding you to copy scriptures.

95
00:04:32,680 --> 00:04:33,839
If you don't change your ways,

96
00:04:34,279 --> 00:04:35,199
you won't leave your courtyard.

97
00:04:35,480 --> 00:04:37,920
Your Highness, you've wronged My Lady!

98
00:04:38,079 --> 00:04:38,720
Xiaotao.

99
00:04:40,720 --> 00:04:41,759
I'm sorry, Wenyue.

100
00:04:42,120 --> 00:04:43,480
I'll obey your orders.

101
00:04:44,680 --> 00:04:46,279
Master Wu,
get your wounds treated first.

102
00:04:46,720 --> 00:04:47,800
As long as I'm here,

103
00:04:48,839 --> 00:04:50,879
no one will dare touch you.

104
00:04:51,279 --> 00:04:52,279
Thank you, Your Highness.

105
00:04:55,639 --> 00:04:56,879
Take him back.

106
00:04:58,160 --> 00:04:58,839
Master.

107
00:05:12,319 --> 00:05:13,639
Dry these flowers properly.

108
00:05:13,680 --> 00:05:14,800
When the Prince returns,

109
00:05:14,839 --> 00:05:16,519
I'll make him flower cakes myself.

110
00:05:22,319 --> 00:05:25,439
Who remembers the tune I played?

111
00:05:31,720 --> 00:05:34,199
Why does the music sound so lifeless?

112
00:05:35,600 --> 00:05:37,120
The Princess Consort is here.

113
00:05:46,040 --> 00:05:47,279
Greetings, Your Highness.

114
00:05:48,439 --> 00:05:49,439
Where is Ruoheng?

115
00:05:56,079 --> 00:05:56,879
My Lady!

116
00:06:01,680 --> 00:06:04,720
Ruoheng, you look terrible.

117
00:06:05,240 --> 00:06:06,360
Send for the physician.

118
00:06:08,439 --> 00:06:10,279
I'm fine, Wenyue.

119
00:06:10,319 --> 00:06:12,879
My Lady hasn't eaten anything.

120
00:06:13,360 --> 00:06:14,160
Ruoheng.

121
00:06:14,879 --> 00:06:16,639
Stop acting like a child.

122
00:06:16,839 --> 00:06:20,279
Focus on getting better
for the Prince's return.

123
00:06:20,519 --> 00:06:22,040
I know I made a mistake.

124
00:06:22,519 --> 00:06:24,720
I delayed your Flower Festival gown.

125
00:06:25,399 --> 00:06:27,199
I'm punishing myself by fasting.

126
00:06:27,480 --> 00:06:30,120
Hoping it will ease your anger.

127
00:06:30,680 --> 00:06:31,920
That's all I ask.

128
00:06:32,279 --> 00:06:34,040
She looks pale from hunger.

129
00:06:34,480 --> 00:06:35,759
Bring her some food.

130
00:06:35,839 --> 00:06:36,639
Yes.

131
00:06:39,279 --> 00:06:41,079
(Her health matters little.)

132
00:06:41,600 --> 00:06:43,879
(But if she can't keep
the Prince's favor,)

133
00:06:44,439 --> 00:06:46,839
(all my efforts will be wasted.)

134
00:06:51,480 --> 00:06:53,639
Since you know you were wrong,

135
00:06:54,279 --> 00:06:54,920
stop

136
00:06:55,399 --> 00:06:57,199
punishing yourself.

137
00:06:57,839 --> 00:07:00,040
Have you forgiven me?

138
00:07:01,959 --> 00:07:02,600
Yes.

139
00:07:02,839 --> 00:07:04,199
Eat well, My Lady.

140
00:07:04,680 --> 00:07:06,160
If Her Highness is pleased,

141
00:07:06,240 --> 00:07:07,680
she might lift your grounding.

142
00:07:22,399 --> 00:07:24,439
Wenyue, let me do that.

143
00:07:50,560 --> 00:07:51,360
Master.

144
00:07:51,879 --> 00:07:52,680
Your hand...

145
00:07:53,680 --> 00:07:55,439
She was so ruthless.

146
00:07:55,879 --> 00:07:58,160
Lin Rulan didn't gain anything either.

147
00:07:58,480 --> 00:07:59,600
She's been grounded.

148
00:07:59,879 --> 00:08:00,680
Shut up.

149
00:08:01,720 --> 00:08:03,160
How's your task going?

150
00:08:04,199 --> 00:08:05,240
It's done.

151
00:08:05,680 --> 00:08:06,959
That old couple

152
00:08:07,279 --> 00:08:09,279
won't cause trouble again.

153
00:08:13,680 --> 00:08:14,639
The priority now

154
00:08:14,639 --> 00:08:16,000
is to lift Miss Rulan's grounding.

155
00:08:16,319 --> 00:08:16,680
Otherwise...

156
00:08:16,680 --> 00:08:17,560
When the Prince returns,

157
00:08:17,560 --> 00:08:18,439
and they consummate the marriage...

158
00:08:18,639 --> 00:08:19,319
She's not a virgin

159
00:08:19,319 --> 00:08:20,120
nor a real lady.

160
00:08:20,279 --> 00:08:21,399
Either one exposed by Wu Lian

161
00:08:21,399 --> 00:08:22,399
is a death sentence.

162
00:08:23,439 --> 00:08:25,040
Let's break into the manor and take her.

163
00:08:25,120 --> 00:08:26,000
Burn Yanyu Embroidery House.

164
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:26,680
No!

165
00:08:27,319 --> 00:08:29,240
All Ruoheng and Rulan's efforts

166
00:08:29,240 --> 00:08:30,160
will be wasted.

167
00:08:30,279 --> 00:08:32,080
More lives will be lost.

168
00:08:33,879 --> 00:08:34,799
Miss Xiaojiu.

169
00:08:35,080 --> 00:08:36,039
Going into the manor now

170
00:08:36,440 --> 00:08:37,919
will only make things worse.

171
00:08:38,279 --> 00:08:39,600
Please pass a message to Lady Cheng'en.

172
00:08:39,799 --> 00:08:40,840
Can one sentence save her?

173
00:08:41,039 --> 00:08:41,679
Exactly.

174
00:08:42,000 --> 00:08:43,639
If Lady Cheng'en helps Wu Lian once,

175
00:08:44,120 --> 00:08:45,399
her grounding will be lifted.

176
00:08:45,840 --> 00:08:46,759
Help Wu Lian?

177
00:08:47,200 --> 00:08:48,399
Since the Princess Consort still needs

178
00:08:48,399 --> 00:08:49,639
Wu Lian's embroidery skills,

179
00:08:49,799 --> 00:08:51,240
helping him once won't hurt.

180
00:08:52,480 --> 00:08:55,159
Mr. Liu, this idea is infuriating.

181
00:08:55,200 --> 00:08:57,279
Lifting her grounding
is the top priority.

182
00:08:58,200 --> 00:09:00,080
Please, Miss Xiaojiu.

183
00:09:07,039 --> 00:09:07,879
Your Highness.

184
00:09:08,440 --> 00:09:11,559
This is my master's embroidery
for the Flower Festival.

185
00:09:15,679 --> 00:09:17,440
Only Master Wu

186
00:09:17,480 --> 00:09:19,759
can create such exquisite beauty.

187
00:09:26,039 --> 00:09:27,480
If you can't embroider,

188
00:09:27,519 --> 00:09:28,759
just rest.

189
00:09:29,519 --> 00:09:30,679
Don't use shoddy work

190
00:09:30,679 --> 00:09:32,120
from unskilled hands

191
00:09:32,240 --> 00:09:33,480
to perfunctory me.

192
00:09:36,080 --> 00:09:37,080
You have a sharp eye, Your Highness.

193
00:09:37,240 --> 00:09:39,440
But my master had no such intention.

194
00:09:39,600 --> 00:09:42,320
I embroidered this

195
00:09:42,440 --> 00:09:43,840
because his hand is injured.

196
00:09:44,279 --> 00:09:45,679
I wanted to show you

197
00:09:45,679 --> 00:09:46,879
that in all Jinxiu City,

198
00:09:47,279 --> 00:09:50,000
no one matches his skill.

199
00:09:50,840 --> 00:09:53,000
Please cure my master's hand,
Your Highness.

200
00:09:53,000 --> 00:09:53,720
Meng Wan.

201
00:09:53,919 --> 00:09:56,000
Don't trouble Her Highness for me.

202
00:09:56,519 --> 00:09:58,679
Didn't I send the manor physician?

203
00:09:59,240 --> 00:10:00,600
With the physician's treatment,

204
00:10:00,879 --> 00:10:02,559
it will take a month

205
00:10:02,639 --> 00:10:04,000
for his hand to fully heal.

206
00:10:04,840 --> 00:10:07,039
But with a divine medicine,

207
00:10:07,440 --> 00:10:09,960
he'll recover in 3 to 5 days.

208
00:10:11,240 --> 00:10:12,559
Where is this divine medicine?

209
00:10:12,879 --> 00:10:14,639
Go find it for him at once.

210
00:10:15,240 --> 00:10:17,279
The physician told me

211
00:10:17,600 --> 00:10:20,720
that Lord Cheng'en was badly burned
in battle

212
00:10:21,120 --> 00:10:22,360
years ago.

213
00:10:22,679 --> 00:10:24,879
A divine healer cured him

214
00:10:25,200 --> 00:10:27,879
in just three days.

215
00:10:28,080 --> 00:10:29,240
I thought

216
00:10:29,519 --> 00:10:31,080
since Lady Cheng'en is his daughter,

217
00:10:31,399 --> 00:10:33,440
she might know about it.

218
00:10:34,080 --> 00:10:34,759
Enough.

219
00:10:35,240 --> 00:10:36,399
I forgive you for the embroidery.

220
00:10:36,519 --> 00:10:38,000
If there's a prescription,

221
00:10:39,600 --> 00:10:41,159
there's nothing I can't get.

222
00:10:41,279 --> 00:10:43,000
Thank you, Your Highness.

223
00:10:43,440 --> 00:10:46,519
Go practice your embroidery more.

224
00:10:47,240 --> 00:10:49,639
Yes.

225
00:10:50,440 --> 00:10:51,240
My Lady.

226
00:10:51,759 --> 00:10:52,559
Why didn't you ask the Princess Consort

227
00:10:52,679 --> 00:10:55,360
to lift your grounding?

228
00:10:56,679 --> 00:10:57,759
What's the point?

229
00:10:58,279 --> 00:11:00,480
Xiaojiu talked to Mr. Liu,

230
00:11:00,720 --> 00:11:02,440
so they must have a new plan.

231
00:11:02,879 --> 00:11:05,159
I want to see

232
00:11:05,159 --> 00:11:08,679
what Master Wu will do next.

233
00:11:37,840 --> 00:11:40,800
♪Night fades before the dawn♪

234
00:11:41,040 --> 00:11:44,040
♪Old vows still guide my hand♪

235
00:11:45,240 --> 00:11:48,000
♪The past no longer binds♪

236
00:11:48,480 --> 00:11:52,200
♪My heart still shines through dust♪

237
00:11:52,640 --> 00:11:56,760
♪Silent blooms, unchanged heart♪

238
00:11:57,600 --> 00:12:00,480
♪Bare hands weave through the frost♪

239
00:12:00,840 --> 00:12:02,840
♪Shadows linger, rain returns♪

240
00:12:02,840 --> 00:12:06,920
♪Honor crowns my weary soul♪

241
00:12:07,320 --> 00:12:09,520
♪For your faith that never broke♪

242
00:12:09,720 --> 00:12:13,840
♪I shattered all the love I knew♪

243
00:12:14,720 --> 00:12:16,640
♪No regrets, no debts unpaid♪

244
00:12:16,640 --> 00:12:20,880
♪At dusk I walk away alone♪

245
00:12:22,080 --> 00:12:24,560
♪If this tale becomes a storm♪

246
00:12:24,680 --> 00:12:27,320
♪Old shadows fade from sight♪

247
00:12:27,320 --> 00:12:29,920
♪One thought turns into ash♪

248
00:12:30,880 --> 00:12:36,240
♪No future left to write♪

249
00:12:37,320 --> 00:12:39,120
♪If I never fall♪

250
00:12:39,160 --> 00:12:41,520
♪How could this waiting end♪

251
00:12:41,520 --> 00:12:42,880
♪If I bear no scars♪

252
00:12:42,880 --> 00:12:45,200
♪How could I challenge fate♪

253
00:12:45,200 --> 00:12:47,560
♪I knew there was no way back♪

254
00:12:47,560 --> 00:12:51,560
♪Yet I left this hope behind♪

255
00:12:51,680 --> 00:12:53,800
♪For your faith that never broke♪

256
00:12:54,000 --> 00:12:57,960
♪I shattered all the love I knew♪

257
00:12:58,920 --> 00:13:00,840
♪No regrets, no debts unpaid♪

258
00:13:00,840 --> 00:13:05,240
♪At dusk I walk away alone♪

259
00:13:06,320 --> 00:13:08,920
♪If this tale becomes a storm♪

260
00:13:08,960 --> 00:13:11,520
♪Old shadows fade from sight♪

261
00:13:11,520 --> 00:13:13,880
♪One thought turns into ash♪

262
00:13:15,000 --> 00:13:20,240
♪No future left to write♪

263
00:13:21,120 --> 00:13:23,520
♪The lamp is out, you're gone♪

264
00:13:24,800 --> 00:13:26,920
♪Heaven and earth fall silent♪

265
00:13:28,600 --> 00:13:30,800
♪If we meet again someday♪

266
00:13:31,240 --> 00:13:37,040
♪This longing sleeps beneath the snow♪
